{"tid":490736,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"(稅貸) 有冇人成功喺華僑永亨自訂息率","createTime":"2017-12-06T01:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T02:39:13.000Z","uid":6604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"51728b439b075a6f5021212330b354b8446793d5","tid":490736,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"12個月還<br />\n之前開 APR 2%<br />\n佢還價要 APR 2.6%<br />\n<br />\n有同事開 APR 2.3%<br />\n佢還價要 APR 3%<br />\n<br />\n佢個APR有啲取巧<br />\n要計埋嗰 3個月 repayment holiday 個 effect<br />\n如果你接受 APR 2.6%<br />\n但你唔用嗰三個 repayment holiday<br />\n實際APR其實係 3.5%<br />\n<br />\n究竟有冇人喺華僑永亨成功自訂稅貸息率 ?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171205/20235364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F20235364&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSablgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=297e97ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F20235364&h=58d99860\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20171205/20235364</a><br />\n吳幗欣續指，該行「自訂息率計劃」反應熱烈，今年平均貸款額按年增加3萬元，達35萬元，而本年平均年利率則約2厘，較去年低十多至二十個點子。<br />\n<br />\n吳幗欣講啲嘢似假喎<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n1. 專業人士<br />\n2. 月薪多過 40K<br />\n3. 其實借嗰筆錢我銀行戶口都有，只不過想借多啲錢買下股"},{"pid":"48eb8e71af06478ca1735bc0dd1ea89a113859d0","tid":490736,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"piss"},{"pid":"5cf05eaac7c5bffe1df91dc786a8ca1fffd919fa","tid":490736,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7524eb4133e3a5252df40a7601d410e56b85bab","tid":490736,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"真係冇人成功 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\